  "texts": [
    "Wise versa, the physics-informed theories can guide and constrain the search space, such as by focusing on specific crystal types or compositions.",
    "This approach accelerates the closed-loop BO process, enabling more targeted and efficient exploration of new battery materials.",
    "One of the main challenges for ML-guided investigation of new battery materials lies in the inefficiency of synthesizing the predicted materials, and difficulty in finding suitable applications.",
    "Thus, the balance of the specificity and the breadth of the research objects is incredibly important.",
    "To overcome this challenge, it is critical to input our human intelligence and more observed experimental objectives into the model as indicated in Fig. 8d, then the results will be more interpretable and valuable."
  ]
